was ever able to break.</i>

194
00:16:04,040 --> 00:16:07,203
<i>Regardless of what method
was used by the Indians,</i>

195
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:10,244
<i>it's a matter of record
that news of the whiskey train</i>

196
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:13,807
<i>became common knowledge within 48 hours</i>

197
00:16:13,920 --> 00:16:19,404
<i>to every tribe of every
North American Plains Indian.</i>

198
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:27,085
<i>We are still unaware why only one tribe
rode out to investigate the firewater train.</i>

199
