492
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:15,211
- What's goin' on over there?
- Singing, sir.

493
00:37:16,240 --> 00:37:18,891
- You have guards at every exit?
- As you ordered, sir.

494
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:22,209
You'd better double the guards.
Check the exits yourself.

495
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:25,210
If they break out of that hall
in marching formation...

496
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:29,041
- That's what happened to Captain Slater.
- Yes, sir.

497
00:37:31,080 --> 00:37:34,129
(Mrs Massingale) Ladies,
our enemy has two heads.

498
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:37,369
First, the enslavement of women by men.

499
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:38,686
(women) Yes.

500
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:41,883
And second, the enslavement
of men themselves

501
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:44,401
by the remorseless tyrant alcohol.

502
00:37:45,520 --> 00:37:48,603
- Are we willing to fight these enemies?
- Yes.

503
00:37:48,720 --> 00:37:50,768
Then we must reach out for freedom,

504
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:53,724
and tear this tyrant from the lips of man.

505
00:37:56,720 --> 00:38:00,122
Now, ladies, I have
an announcement to make

506
00:38:00,240 --> 00:38:03,642
to each and every one of you
who has touched my heart.

507
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:08,129
The time has come for me to say goodbye
to all you wonderful women...

508
00:38:08,240 --> 00:38:09,685
Thank God!

509
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:13,088
Something has occurred
which requires my presence elsewhere.

510
00:38:13,200 --> 00:38:17,364
- I am going to the city of Denver.
- Denver?

511
00:38:17,720 --> 00:38:21,281
I know, I know. You ask me
"Why Denver?" I'll tell you why.

512
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:24,722
Because 40 wagons of whiskey
are going to Denver right now.

513
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:29,129
40 wagons of poison
for those poor misguided citizens,

514
00:38:29,240 --> 00:38:31,322
and no one in high office seems to care.

515
00:38:31,440 --> 00:38:33,169
Well, <i>I</i> do!

516
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:35,442
And I shall shout it over and over

517
00:38:35,560 --> 00:38:40,168
until the mountains of Colorado come
tumbling down to the Denver saloons.

518
00:38:41,560 --> 00:38:44,166
- Will your hearts go with me?
- Yes!

519
00:38:44,680 --> 00:38:47,445
- Is our cause just and righteous?
- Yes!

520
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:53,604
- I've doubled the guards, sir.
- I want you to guard the main entrance.

521
00:38:53,720 --> 00:38:56,849
- Do I have your blessings?
- Yes!

522
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:58,007
No!

523
00:38:58,120 --> 00:39:01,329
No! I cannot let you go
to that sinful city alone.

524
00:39:01,920 --> 00:39:06,244
If you'll have me, Mrs Massingale,
I'll go with you.

525
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:11,843
Get over there.
Drag my daughter off that platform.

526
00:39:14,400 --> 00:39:17,165
Oh, how wonderful, ladies!

527
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:20,648
- Oh, ladies, we'll all go to Denver.
- Yes!

528
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:24,970
- We'll make it our marching song.
- Yes!

