639
00:49:31,320 --> 00:49:33,288
♪ Stand up...

640
00:49:33,760 --> 00:49:39,051
<i>it might be prudent right at this moment to
get our bearings upon this historic arena.</i>

641
00:49:39,400 --> 00:49:41,209
<i>Julesburg is</i> here.

642
00:49:41,320 --> 00:49:45,245
<i>To the southwest along the South
Platte River is the city of Denver.</i>

643
00:49:45,360 --> 00:49:47,601
<i>North of it we find Fort Russell.</i>

644
00:49:47,720 --> 00:49:51,486
<i>The Wallingham wagon train
had moved to this point on the river.</i>

645
00:49:51,600 --> 00:49:55,002
<i>The first cavalry patrol
under Captain Slater - here.</i>

646
00:49:55,120 --> 00:49:58,363
<i>The second cavalry patrol
under Colonel Gearhan'</i> - here,

647
00:49:58,480 --> 00:50:01,211
<i>with, of course,
the temperance marchers.</i>

648
00:50:01,320 --> 00:50:04,051
<i>And the band of Sioux Indians</i> - here.

649
00:50:05,400 --> 00:50:08,961
<i>In the city of Denver, another
miners' meeting was being held.</i>

650
00:50:28,000 --> 00:50:31,004
Hold it! Hold it down.
This meetin' is called to order.

651
00:50:31,120 --> 00:50:35,045
Tell me who called this meetin', what for,
and what's all the hollering about!

652
00:50:35,160 --> 00:50:37,686
I did. Clayton, we gotta face the facts.

653
00:50:37,800 --> 00:50:41,122
There's been no word from
that wagon train in two weeks.

654
00:50:41,240 --> 00:50:44,642
- That's right.
- There's snow already at Grizzly Pass.

655
00:51:06,800 --> 00:51:10,441
- Afternoon, gents.
- Oracle, the thing is we, uh...

656
00:51:10,560 --> 00:51:12,528
- We got trouble.
- You know?

657
00:51:12,640 --> 00:51:15,041
That wagon train
may not never get to you.

658
00:51:15,160 --> 00:51:17,606
- Why not?
- Why, thank you.

659
00:51:21,080 --> 00:51:26,564
It was all set on comin' to me.
I, uh... I was lookin' up and, uh... uh...

660
00:51:26,680 --> 00:51:28,648
Thank you.

661
00:51:28,760 --> 00:51:31,286
<i>♪ Hallelu...</i>

662
00:51:31,400 --> 00:51:33,562
- There! Now I see it!
