I see hundreds of lnjuns.

665
00:51:44,200 --> 00:51:46,248
You see anything else, Oracle?

666
00:51:46,360 --> 00:51:49,284
- I think, uh...
- <i>♪ Hallelu...</i>

667
00:51:49,400 --> 00:51:53,246
- I see men... I see men on the march.
- Cavalry?

668
00:51:53,360 --> 00:51:56,170
Course not. This ain't no time for children.

669
00:51:56,280 --> 00:51:59,045
I see men, men carryin', uh...

670
00:52:01,080 --> 00:52:03,481
picks and, uh...

671
00:52:03,600 --> 00:52:06,968
axes and, uh... uh...

672
00:52:10,800 --> 00:52:12,768
uh...

673
