685
00:53:19,800 --> 00:53:23,441
<i>The Denver citizens' militia
was making an easterly crossing</i>

686
00:53:23,560 --> 00:53:25,483
<i>of the South Platte River,</i>

687
00:53:25,600 --> 00:53:29,286
