688
00:53:30,280 --> 00:53:33,170
<i>picking up more braves all the time.</i>

689
00:53:34,920 --> 00:53:36,001
Whoa!

690
00:53:37,360 --> 00:53:40,842
For the beloved love of all the saints,
St Pat and Mike and Bridget,

691
00:53:40,960 --> 00:53:44,043
and all the souls in purgatory, not again!

692
00:53:45,040 --> 00:53:47,930
Call yourself a wagon!
You rotten collection of wood!

693
00:53:48,040 --> 00:53:50,850
You ain't fit for carryin' swill to vultures!

694
00:54:10,920 --> 00:54:12,888
Whoa!

695
00:54:13,680 --> 00:54:18,891
All right, O'Flaherty. What's your excuse
this time, you ignorant immigrant lump?

696
00:54:22,200 --> 00:54:25,124
Oh, lump, is it? Well...

697
00:54:27,840 --> 00:54:31,845
All things being equal,
we'll be havin' a word with your lordship.

698
00:54:31,960 --> 00:54:34,884
I told you I am not a lordship!

699
00:54:35,000 --> 00:54:38,482
Can't expect an Irish serf to forget
the habits of a lifetime, now.

700
00:54:38,600 --> 00:54:41,080
- Just get on with it.
- Well, now.

