802
01:03:08,440 --> 01:03:12,286
<i>circle around whole wagon train,
come in from southeast,</i>

803
01:03:12,400 --> 01:03:15,927
<i>grab last three wagons
and go like hell... west.</i>

804
01:03:17,080 --> 01:03:22,086
<i>In the morning, when the sun rises
over iron Mountain two hands high,</i>

805
01:03:23,080 --> 01:03:25,048
<i>attack!</i>

806
01:03:26,840 --> 01:03:30,890
<i>If Long Knives capture braves,
show them paper.</i>

807
01:03:31,000 --> 01:03:33,446
<i>We good Indians. No trouble.</i>

808
01:03:34,680 --> 01:03:36,921
<i>Go back to reservation.</i>

809
01:03:37,040 --> 01:03:40,601
<i>But before you go,
don't forget to ask for presents.</i>

810
